  m_text: "1) You can move the camera by: WASD, right click and drag, zoom out and
    in. \n\n2) Use the Compass in the top right corner to move rooms. If there are
    enemies in the room, all must be eliminated before progressing to the next room.
    \n\n3) All actions cost stamina, represented as blue stars in the bottom left
    UI. Movement costs stamina aswell, in a 1 to 1 ratio of tile to stamina.\n\n\n\n"
